arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerDonan = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_DONAN_FOLLOWER)
	
	--Donan to Static
	Hydra.QActorEnableAI(followerDonan, false)
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerDonan)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerDonan, LOC_DONAN_TOWER, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerDonan, LOC_DONAN_TOWER)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerDonan)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerDonan)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_DONAN_TOWER)
	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_TAISSA_01, ID_DONAN_TOWER, ID_TAISSA_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, CONVO_TAISSA_01)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_TAISSA_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, "VERGE_TAISSA_INTRO")
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	--Static Run from A to B
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_POST, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_POST)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_TOWER, "QST_VERGE02_FIN")
		
	--Static Run from A to B
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_POST, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_POST)
		
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	--Donan Bark
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_VILLAGER_01, ID_VILLAGER)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_VILLAGER, CONVO_VILLAGER_01)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_VILLAGER)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_TOWN, "VERGE_DONAN_INTRO")
	
end
